Package: FastHierarchicalClust
Type: Package
Title: Hierarchical Agglomerative Clustering (HAC)
Version: 0.1.0
Date: 2025-04-10
Author: Janikson Garcia Brito
Maintainer: Janikson Garcia <janikson.garcia07@gmail.com>
Description: Implementation of Hierarchical Agglomerative Clustering (HAC) in R and Rcpp. The package includes optimized algorithms to improve computational complexity, with comparisons between different approaches. A simulation file is provided to evaluate performance and complexity.
